  "section_name": "Investment Recommendation & Outlook",
  "text": "Despite near-term challenges, several fundamental strengths support a constructive long-term view. Adobe generates exceptional cash flow with a free cash flow margin of 50.47% (K011), highlighting the capital-light nature of its business model. The company maintains substantial R&D investment at 17.73% of revenue in Q4 (K007, C018), reflecting commitment to advancing AI-powered capabilities across Creative Cloud. Analyst sentiment remains constructive, with RBC Capital reiterating an Outperform rating and $480 price target in August 2025, citing long-term AI monetization upside (Recent Developments summary, C015).",
